Today on the show we ran back our interview with Rush Limbaugh, which was definitely a debate conversation but much needed. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought of the conversation and Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to our celebrity and chief Donald Trump.
